                                    <h4 class="recommendation-title">UX Design in 2025</h4>
                                    <p class="recommendation-excerpt">New approaches to intuitive user experiences.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="recommendation-link">Read article â†’</a>
                                </div>
                            </article>
                        </div>
